high_descs: Walk forward to the safe, then turn left and walk to the blue armchair.
Pick up the key chain in front of the remote control on the armchair.
Turn right and walk slightly forward to the tall lamp in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Examine a key chain by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Cross the room and when you get to the sofa, head left to stand in front of the blue chair.
Pick up the leftmost set of keys from the chair.
Turn right to carry the keys closer to the lamp, which is between the chair and sofa.
Turn on the lamp to look at the keys.
anns.task_desc: Look at keys using an illuminated lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and hang a left to walk to the blue armchair.
Pick up the leftmost keys from the blue armchair.
Turn to face the tall lamp on the right.
anns.task_desc: Look at some keys under the light of a tall lamp.
